			<p>
				<a
					href="https://support.exotel.com/support/solutions/articles/3000104288-call-centre-dashboard-private-beta-updated-"
				>
					A dashboard for clients to see the analytics live in a
					glance.
				</a>
			</p>
			<p>
				We developed a React based dashboard with graphs for most
				important live information and tables/cards for other
				information. It is powered by a go API service serving analytics
				from MongoDB, another go service was consuming events from a
				Kafka cluster where all the services were sending events and
				either putting it directly in MongoDB for live stats or
				aggregating it in 5mins chunks for historical stats.
			</p>
			<p>
				It allowed the account admins to get an idea of what is
				happening in their contact center at a glance. They could also
				get more granular and differently categorized data to assess
				their agent's and team's performance by following cross links
				which preserved applied date, group and agent filters.
			</p>
