				browser tabs. On receiving an event it pushed the notification
				to the relevant user's browser, which was picked up by the
				frontend code and <a
					href="https://support.exotel.com/support/solutions/articles/45252-what-notifications-do-i-get-for-calls-and-where-do-they-show-up-"
				>
					shown to the user on the website</a
				> and as a <a
					href="https://support.exotel.com/support/solutions/articles/121442-enabilng-desktop-notifications"
					>desktop notification.</a
				>
			</p>
